-- Google Aims to Boost Its Video, Banner Ad Business in China, FT Reports
-- B y   V i c t o r i a   B a t c h e l o r
-- 2010-12-06T23:09:24Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2010-12-06/google-aims-to-boost-video-banner-ad-business-in-china-ft-says.html
Google Inc. aims to expand in China
its business of placing video and banner advertisements on other
websites following the loss of online search market share in the
Asian nation, the Financial Times reported, citing an interview
with John Liu, the company’s vice president for greater China
operations.  Liu said the company has “good traffic” in China and
revenue is growing quarter on quarter, the FT reported.  To contact the reporter on this story:
